==Dutch==

===Personal pronoun===
[[Category:Dutch personal pronouns]]
'''jullie''' (''mute form'' '''[[je]]''', ''reflexive form'' '''[[je]]''', ''possessive form'' '''jullie''')
# ''Second-person plural, subjective:'' [[you]].
#: ''Zijn jullie klaar?'' &mdash; Are you (''plural'') ready?
# ''Second-person plural, objective:'' [[you]].
#: ''Ik zal het aan jullie geven.'' &mdash; I will give it to you (''plural'').
#: ''Dit zal niet werken voor jullie.'' &mdash; This won't work for you (''plural'').

